            <div style="margin: 0px 137px;">
              <p>The goal of this project is to expand snow sport accessibility through the use of our 
                matching service.</p>
              <p>Our team of snow sport enthusiasts decided to create a platform which joins the skiers
                 and snowboarders of Boulder Colorado through a matching service designed to make rides, 
                 partners, mountains, and friends easily accessible, so everyone can get as much time in 
                 the snow as possible. Many college students do not have access to cars or rides to 
                 mountains during the winter season, putting a damper on their ski/snowboard season, 
                 but we offer a solution to this problem. Our matching service is based on user chosen 
                 tags, so that we can find the perfect person to fit your ski sessions, whether you are 
                 just looking for a ride, or a friend to ski with, we aim to accommodate all your personal 
                 preferences so that our valued users can be as comfortable as possible while enjoying the 
